01:41.040 --> 01:45.320
accessible energy systems.

01:45.320 --> 01:51.040
But as much as energy has benefited the world, it's also had unintended consequences.

01:51.040 --> 01:56.600
We're all aware of the challenges and dangers posed by climate change.

01:56.600 --> 02:03.320
