06:02.400 --> 06:11.720
have maybe 30-meter tall trees that fall down and crush the wall of the house.

06:11.720 --> 06:19.480
And today, as we speak right now in California, there are also strong atmospheric river events

06:19.520 --> 06:21.520
right now.

06:21.520 --> 06:29.080
